/* ===== COMPARATIVE CONSTRUCTIONS ===== */

<comparative-construction> ::= <comparative-than> | <comparative-from> | <equality-comparison> | <proportional-comparison>

<comparative-than> ::= <adjective-comparative> "než" <noun-phrase>

